  "detailed_description": "Path Weaver is a unique puzzle game that harbours a variety of different concepts and themes. Drag and drop the elements that are given to you in each chapter to create the desired outcome.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911520/extras/e8aa62339ba4047ba5512a6a060ad56a.poster.avif?t=1716186314\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911520/extras/e8aa62339ba4047ba5512a6a060ad56a.webm?t=1716186314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911520/extras/e8aa62339ba4047ba5512a6a060ad56a.mp4?t=1716186314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Some chapters will give you hints on how to solve them. Use them to your advantage or test your skill by figuring things out yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911520/extras/34e89d1e6d6165a545b88ecf14cfb78d.poster.avif?t=1716186314\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911520/extras/34e89d1e6d6165a545b88ecf14cfb78d.webm?t=1716186314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911520/extras/34e89d1e6d6165a545b88ecf14cfb78d.mp4?t=1716186314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore various concepts and overcome the challenges to progress your Path!",
